narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Not too many choices at PKU, but definitely worthwhile. A bit esoteric at times and often very unstructured, but an intriguing take on Chinese law.
it offers some insight into chinese culture. presentations are a good opportunity to learn more. lectures are not organized though
